## Recurring Pattern Field

A field that captures a recurring schedule (daily / weekly / monthly with interval, weekday selection, and end date).

### Usage

```ts
import { CardDef, field, contains } from 'https://cardstack.com/base/card-api';
import RecurringPatternField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/recurring-pattern/recurring-pattern';

export class Example extends CardDef {
  @field schedule = contains(RecurringPatternField, {
    configuration: { defaultFrequency: 'weekly' },
  });
}
```

See the **Examples** section of this spec for the full set of supported configuration options.
